{"id":591734,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/08/【图说天朝】只是单纯疫苗问题-请勿上升政治高度/","date":"2018-08-04T09:41:56Z","modified":"2018-08-04T09:41:56Z","title":"【图说天朝】只是单纯疫苗问题 请勿上升政治高度","content":"<p>8月4日，一张疑似疫苗受害者微信群聊截图流传网络，一名受害者家属似乎对其他群成员议论政治，推广“普世价值”而感到不满，发言称“疫苗问题勿上升至政治高度，勿谈普世价值观，我们虽然是受害者，但一样爱国”。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/DjvnPbcU8AA3y9f.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-591735\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/DjvnPbcU8AA3y9f.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/DjvnPbcU8AA3y9f.jpg 506w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/08/DjvnPbcU8AA3y9f-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[14218,8772,14238,8782,10435,9465,35249,8623,9325,35322,35252,35328,12010]}